In $\triangle ABC$, what is the value of $x + y$? [asy]
import olympiad;
size(7cm);

pair a = dir(76);
pair b = (-1, 0);
pair c = (1, 0);
pair o = (0, 0);

draw(a--b--c--cycle);
draw(a--o);

