draw((0,2)--(6,2));
draw((3,0)--(3,2));
draw((2,2)--(2,5));
draw((4,2)--(4,5));
[/asy]

ground_truth.solution:
Let $x$ and $y$ be the width and length of one of the five rectangles, respectively.

[asy]
unitsize(0.6 cm);

draw((0,0)--(6,0)--(6,5)--(0,5)--cycle);
draw((0,2)--(6,2));
draw((3,0)--(3,2));
draw((2,2)--(2,5));
